{"title":"「BestCoder Round #88」Tree Cutting（改）","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["BestCoder","树形 DP","FWT","DP"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6272#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6272","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6272/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6272/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6272"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给一棵 $n(1 \\le n \\le 1000)$ 个节点的树，每个点有点权 $w_i(0 \\le w_i < 2 ^ {15})$ 。\r\n\r\n设 $f_x$ 表示树上有多少个连通块，满足点权异或和为 $x$ 。\r\n\r\n求 $f_0, f_1, f_2, ..., f_{2 ^ {15} - 1}$ 对 $998244353$ 取模。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个正整数 $n$ 。\r\n\r\n第二行 $n$ 个非负整数 $w_i$ 。\r\n\r\n接下来 $n-1$ 行，每行两个正整数 $x, y$ ，表示树上存在边 $(x, y)$ 。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一行，共 $2 ^ {15}$ 个非负整数，依次为 $f_0, f_1, ..., f_{2 ^ {15} - 1}$ 。"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，$1 \\le n \\le 1000, 0 \\le w_i < 2 ^ {15}$ 。"}]}